292→  <p class="description animate" style="--i:2">
293→    Every push to <code>main</code> triggers the full pipeline. Tests and linting run in parallel,
294→    then the build step produces a Docker image. Staging deploys automatically; production requires
295→    manual approval via a GitHub environment gate.
296→  </p>
297→
298→  <div class="mermaid-wrap animate" style="--i:3">
299→    <div class="zoom-controls">
300→      <button onclick="zoomDiagram(this, 1.2)" title="Zoom in">+</button>
301→      <button onclick="zoomDiagram(this, 0.8)" title="Zoom out">&minus;</button>
302→      <button onclick="resetZoom(this)" title="Reset zoom">&#8634;</button>
303→    </div>
304→    <pre class="mermaid">
305→      graph TD
306→        A[Push to main] --> B{Branch?}
307→        B -->|main| C[Run Tests]
308→        B -->|feature| I[Run Tests]
309→        I --> J[Preview Deploy]
310→        C --> D[Lint + Type Check]
311→        C --> E[Unit Tests]
312→        C --> F[Integration Tests]
313→        D --> G[Build Docker Image]
314→        E --> G
315→        F --> G
316→        G --> H[Deploy to Staging]
317→        H --> K{Smoke Tests Pass?}
318→        K -->|Yes| L[Manual Approval]
319→        K -->|No| M[Alert + Rollback]
320→        L --> N[Deploy to Production]
321→        N --> O[Health Check]
322→        O --> P[Done]
