328→    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-swatch" style="background:var(--tertiary)"></div> Decision gate</div>
329→    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-swatch" style="background:var(--danger)"></div> Failure path</div>
330→    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-swatch" style="background:var(--secondary)"></div> Success</div>
331→  </div>
