333→  <div class="callout animate" style="--i:5">
334→    <strong>ELK layout.</strong> The <code>layout: 'elk'</code> engine provides better node positioning
335→    for complex graphs — it requires the separate <code>@mermaid-js/layout-elk</code> package (imported above).
336→    Without it, Mermaid silently falls back to dagre.
337→  </div>
